209
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:38,010
♪Midnight air feels ambiguous,
slightly intoxicating♪

210
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:43,110
♪Lighting flickers,
blurred you into mystery♪

211
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:48,400
♪Please use love to sentence me
to life imprisonment♪

212
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:53,560
♪Fingertips, your eyes,
movements, expressions♪

213
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:58,620
♪Every detail attracts me♪

214
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:04,090
♪The rhythm of the hot dance,
restless heart♪

215
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:09,270
♪How can I stay calm, almost revealing
my uncontrollable feelings♪

216
00:15:09,270 --> 00:15:12,550
♪Be an outlaw of love♪

217
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:15,190
♪Want to possess all of you♪

218
00:15:15,190 --> 00:15:19,660
♪Imprison you
in the depths of my heart♪

219
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:23,070
♪Be an outlaw of love♪

220
00:15:23,070 --> 00:15:25,610
♪Don't need your forgiveness♪

